text: Urban Laguna also known as Laguna Urban Corridor is a proposal metropolitan urban area planning in the province of Laguna composing six cities of Biñan, Cabuyao, Calamba, San Pedro, Santa Rosa and San Pablo and three towns of Bay, Calauan and Los Baños situated at the western vicinity of province respectively. It is situated adjacent south of Metro Manila the capital region of the Philippines.https://tuklas.up.edu.ph/Record/UP-99796217612698578Its administrative center is Santa Rosa and the largest city is Calamba. ==Largest cities== ==Related pages== * Metro Batangas * Metro Lucena ==Reference== Category:Settlements in the Philippines Category:Laguna (province)
